  [Excerpts] The 10-person Cuban delegation that will handle 
the Ibero- American summit on 14-15 June arrived in Cartagena 48 
hours ago. [passage omitted] 
  The first official activity before the Ibero-American summit 
concluded this weekend; it was the scientific conference on 
sustainable development. Our chief representative was Dr. Rosa 
Elena Simeon Negrin, minister of science, technology, and 
