<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Rudan (Hormozgan), June 5, (IRNA) -- Unidentified 
gunmen kidnapped a Chinese national and two Iranians in this 
southern province on Friday. 
  Fu Weixian, who worked for a mineral factory, was abducted 
by 
armed men along with his driver and another Iranian accompanying 
him. 
  The car in which the Chinese national and his Iranian 
companions were travelling was found on Saturday around Heights 
city. 
  Efforts are underway to track down the kidnappers and free 
the victims. 

