  [Text] Yesterday afternoon the Thai ambassador in Tehran 
was summoned to the Foreign ministry and handed a note of 
protest by the deputy foreign minister and head of the 
Department for Southern and Eastern Affairs. The Central News 
Unit reports this note protested the arrest of several Iranians 
on the trumped-up charges of their attempting to blow up the 
