  [Text] Xiao Zeban, a member of the All-China Federation of 
Trade Unions Secretariat, has underscored the importance of 
coordinating Chinese and Cuban labor union efforts to obtain 
greater success. The Chinese labor union leader made this 
statement today, during a meeting in Havana between the high 
