    [Editorial Report] The following is a compilation of 
reports on the activities of members of the Politburo of the 
Central Committee of the Communist Party of Cuba monitored from 
Havana radio and television sources in Spanish between 30 May 
and 5 June. 
  Division General Cintra Frias has visited the Western Army 
and pointed out the intense efforts that it is making to become 
the best command within the Revolutionary Armed Forces of Cuba. 
(Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1409 GMT 31 May 94) 
