researchers. (Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in 
Spanish 0000 GMT 1 Jun 94) 
  Pedro Ross Leal has chaired the economic efficiency assembly 
of the workers of the Electronic Equipment Production Complex in 
Havana. Ross stressed that the necessary measures will require 
in-depth analysis and awareness. (Havana Radio Rebelde Network 
in Spanish 1700 GMT 3 Jun 94) 

