<H3> <TI>   Toussaint Consults Legislators on Priorities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Toussaint Consults Legislators on Priorities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL0806163294 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio in French 1030 
GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>

